text: Allison Joy Langer (born May 22, 1974) is an American TV and movie actress. She acted as Rayanne Graff in the drama show My So-Called Life. Langer also acted as Erica Warner in the TV show Private Practice. She was born in Columbus, Ohio.A. J. Langer Biography (1974-) She moved to the San Fernando Valley with her family at age five. ==References== Category:American television actors Category:Actors from Ohio Category:1974 births Category:Living people
